framework, w3 will transfer noise to the shared bases {l2, l3}, which will in turn negatively affect the models parameterized by w1 and w2.

One might consider the naive combination of the shared basis model (3) and AMTL (4) to prevent negative transfer among latent features where the task parameter matrix is decomposed into LS in (4):

